videos.description: Brett Reed knocks down the 3-pointer off the inbound pass at the buzzer to end the half against Notre Dame.
videos.headline: Chaminade hits buzzer beater to end the half

videos.description: Matt Farrell creates space at the free throw line and knocks down a jumper early against Chaminade.
videos.headline: Farrell hits quick jumper for Irish

videos.description: Bonzie Colson regains his dribble and creates space to knock down a quick two for the Irish.
videos.headline: Colson spins to make jumper

videos.description: Austin Pope crashes the boards on a missed 3-pointer off the rim and jams it with two hands.
videos.headline: Pope slams home putback for Chaminade

videos.description: Nikola Djogo is all by himself on the fast break and misses on the two-handed attempt.
videos.headline: Djogo misses wide-open dunk
